Why WestEnd
WestEnd Advisors is an independent, institutional asset management firm managing $3.0 billion* in assets under management and advisement as of June 30, 2017. Since 1996, we have developed and refined a proprietary, qualitative investment process that translates economic data analysis into thoughtful investment decisions.  For two decades, this approach has enabled us to navigate a wide variety of market conditions on behalf of our clients. 

 
* Total firm assets under management and advisement include $2.1 billion of assets in Unified Managed Account (UMA) programs for which WestEnd provides model portfolios but has no discretion to effect trades and no supervisory responsibility over the assets in the program. This number has been derived from the most recent information provided by each of the participating UMA programs and may not be current as of the date stated above. This information is included as supplemental information only.


 

